README:
GAZE_PRF By : Martin Szinte
With : Gilles de Hollander, Marco Aqil, Serge Dumoulin & Tomas Knapen
## Experiment description Experiment in which we first used a full screen 4 direction (left/right/up/down) bar pass stimuli in a attetion to fixation or attention to the bar experiment. Next, we use the same tasks using a bar pass restricted to an aperture and displayed at 3 different position surrounding the fixation target put at the screen center or displaced to the left or to the right.
